---
import { Picture } from "@astrojs/image/components";
import Container from "../components/container.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About us">
  <Container>
    <div class="mb-8">
      <div class="bg-darkblue rounded-lg h-80 md:max-h-92 overflow-hidden">
        <Picture
          src="class.png"
          alt="hire.png"
          sizes="(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px"
          widths={[200, 400, 800, 1200, 1800]}
          aspectRatio="16:9"
          background="#ffffff"
          fit="cover"
          position="center"
          class="rounded-t-lg opacity-70 overflow-hidden"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
    <h1
      class="mb-4 text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl"
    >
      <span
        class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r to-blue-300 from-blue-700"
        >Volunteer
      </span> with New World Steelpan Orchestra
    </h1>

    <p class="pb-5">
      Join Our Team of Volunteers, volunteering your time with New World Steel
      Pan Orchestra is a great way to make a difference in your community while
      having fun and learning new skills. Our volunteers play a crucial role in
      helping us plan events, fundraise, and spread the word about our
      organization. Whether you're interested in event planning, marketing, or
      outreach, we have a volunteer opportunity that's right for you. By joining
      our team, you'll be part of a dynamic and passionate group of individuals
      who share a common goal of promoting Caribbean music and culture.
    </p>
    <p class="pb-5">
      Attending our events is not only a great way to enjoy Caribbean music and
      culture, but also to support our cause. Our events are a celebration of
      the vibrant and diverse Caribbean culture, featuring live performances by
      our talented musicians and dancers. By attending our events, you'll help
      us raise awareness and funds to sustain our organization and continue
      promoting Caribbean music and culture. Plus, you'll have a great time
      dancing, socializing, and experiencing the joy and energy of the steel pan
      music.
    </p>
    <p class="pb-5">
      Attend Our Events, Spread the Word, One of the easiest and most effective
      ways to support New World Steel Pan Orchestra is by spreading the word
      about our organization. Whether you share our social media posts, tell
      your friends and family about us, or simply wear one of our t-shirts or
      hats, you can help raise awareness and support for our cause. By spreading
      the word, you'll help us reach new audiences and engage more people in our
      mission to promote Caribbean music and culture. Every little bit helps,
      and we appreciate your support in any form.
    </p>
  </Container>
</Layout>
